OL,4,G0955FFind It, Fix It, Flog It
OL,5,     GThe boys rummage through the
OL,6,     Ghangar of a Vulcan bomber. Henry
OL,7,     GCole restores a cockpit seat,
OL,8,     Gwhile Simon O'Brien attempts to
OL,9,     Gturn part of a jet engine into a
OL,10,     Gcoffee table.
OL,11,G1055FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GEnvironmentally-friendly couple
OL,13,     GIan and Jayne host first, at The
OL,14,     GSchool House B&B in Pencader,
OL,15,     GWales. At dinner, eyebrows are
OL,16,     Graised at two straight-talking
OL,17,     Gguests.
